item.title: About
item.description: About Me 📱 iOS Developer since 2012 🤖, live in Melbourne work at iflix. I feel lucky 🍀 my job is also my hobby 💻. I like to break things fast 💔 and fix things faster 🚀. After work, I also enjoy video games 🎮 and videography 📷.
